m>Footloose</em>舞蹈以及组织几场快闪活动。 </p><figure id="attachment_3608847" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3608847" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3608847" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/footloose-kevin-bacon@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/footloose-kevin-bacon@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/footloose-kevin-bacon@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/footloose-kevin-bacon@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/footloose-kevin-bacon@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/footloose-kevin-bacon@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/footloose-kevin-bacon@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3608847" class="wp-caption-text">凯文·培根 1984 年的影片《自由自在》。图片来源：哥伦比亚广播公司（CBS），盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p><em>《浑身解数》于 1984 年上映，由培根</em>主演，饰演芝加哥少年伦·麦考马克 (Ren McCormack)，他搬到一个小镇，向当地部长发起挑战，要求推翻舞蹈禁令。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kevin-bacon-to-return-to-footloose-high-school-to-attend-prom-3608844">在学生们长达数月的活动之后，凯文·培根重返“自由自在”高中参加舞会的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
